<h1>Schedule of Loss</h1>
<p><strong>{{brand_name}}</strong> - {{claim_label}}</p>

<hr>

<p><strong>Claimant:</strong> {{claimant_name}}</p>
<p><strong>Defendant:</strong> {{defendant_name}}</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <th align="left">Description</th>
    <th align="left">Amount</th>
  </tr>
  {{#each line_items}}
  <tr>
    <td>{{description}}</td>
    <td>{{currency amount}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/each}}
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Total before court fee</strong></td>
    <td><strong>{{currency total_claim_amount}}</strong></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Court issue fee estimate</td>
    <td>{{currency court_fee}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Total including issue fee</strong></td>
    <td><strong>{{currency total_with_fees}}</strong></td>
  </tr>
</table>

{{#if claim_interest}}
<h2>Interest requested for review</h2>
<p>
  Interest has been marked for review. Current reference rate: {{interest_rate}}% per year.
  Daily interest reference figure: {{currency daily_interest}}.
</p>
{{/if}}

<p>
  Court fees are payable directly to HMCTS when filing. The court may add the issue fee to the judgment
  if the claim succeeds.
</p>
